rComments: Professor Grammond is one of the best teachers I have ever had and I only have positive things to say about him. He is extremely fair, open-minded and is always willing to answer students questions. He is a tough grader, but as long as you listen in class everything should be fine!!
Je me considère extrêmement chanceuse d'avoir eu ce professeur. Il est passionné par sa matière, ce qui rend les cours très intéressants! D'autant plus, ses explications sont claires et précises.

He is fair as mentioned. He is very very specific.. you either will get the points or you won't. This is what I gathered from others and myself. As a Professor, he is beyond qualified and an excellent teacher - although the material itself is a bit dry. Wish I had him in contracts! Excellent Prof, would take again!
He's fair. Lectures start off great but get more and more dry as the semester goes on. For the exam, pinpoint references within the cases are essential to getting marks
Very nice, organized and knowledgeable person. Do your readings if you wanna understand what's said in class. Gives good feedback on assignments and very lenient grader.
I learned  so much just by going to his classes.  He really took the time during class to answer everybody's questions.  Plus, he gave EXCELLENT feedback on VCampus assignments.

Cannot be recommended highly enough.  Smart, nice, incredibly clear.  He'll expect REALLY good answers on the finals and will give you complex questions, but isn't that what Obligations is all about?  Take him to really learn the stuff, you'll be thankful later.
